excerpt: "Want to make your LinkedIn posts stand out? Learn how to make text bold on LinkedIn without any special tools. This guide covers the manual Unicode method and more."
coverImage: "/blog/images/make-text-bold-linkedin-cover.jpg"
author: "The MarkdownToLinkedIn Team"
